{"tid":1481851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大衛vs歌利亞與香港人vs暴政, 香港人係贏撚硬!!","createTime":"2019-08-18T01:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T02:50:43.000Z","uid":118082,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3f2d482f2f5558107fe6598db35e27d6cbed65","tid":1481851,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:12:48.000Z","msg":"好耐之前, 有一個細路, 佢叫大衛<br />\n佢對面既係當時第一勇士, 戰無不勝而且身高三米既歌利亞<br />\n<br />\n跟時d人點睇呢場決戰呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大部分人 : 歌利亞2下就打撚死大衛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大衛陣營既好友 : 大衛雖然勁但對手仲厲害, 如果攬炒就當贏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大衛 : 我贏撚硬, 因為耶和華就係我既背後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果係大衛用左幾粒石春, 就打敗左歌利亞, 仲批左佢個頭落黎當凳坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日, 有班細路行出黎面對既係暴政極權。<br />\n佢地有不亞當年大衛既信念, 所以結果只有一個, 就係:<br />\n<br />\n香港人, 贏撚硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n從6月以來一場又一場既抗爭, 我地都有足夠既智慧, 仁愛, 勇氣去跨越極權既陰謀同陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n你, 願意同呢班細路一齊對抗暴政嗎?!<br />\n<br />\n天祐吾城, 光復香港, 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n818, 維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n耶撚們返完教會, 都要出黎呀!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539798799bce6182a0acd67808595e44e20cd1ce","tid":1481851,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:13:15.000Z","msg":"十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3c84c266e080d7aa7f962b4b3623e87085a715","tid":1481851,"